chmod
change permission for file & folder

CMD:	chmod goupNameOperatorPermission file/folder
e.g.:	chmod g+x fileName
	
	groupName:
	u: user
	g: group
	o: other

	operator:
	+: add
	-: remove

	permission:
	r: (4) read 
	w: (2) wirte
	x: (1) execute for file, access for folder


CMD:	chmod permission(int) -Option file/folder
e.g.:	chmod 777 -R fileName
	777: 
		first for user
		second for group
		thrid for other

	-R: recursive for files inside the directory includeing the directory
	*: wildcard for files inside directory



